      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Back with a Vengeance",
        "Client": "Admiral Galleus",
        "Description": "A variant of Magnamalo has appeared.\r\nYour Master Hamon seems especially\r\nupset about its existence. Kamura has\r\nformally requested that you deal with\r\nthis threat. \u003CPL\u003E, you must\r\nprotect your homeland by eliminating\r\nthat vengeful beast. Go get it done.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Scorned Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Retour en force",
        "Client": "Amiral Galleus",
        "Description": "Un variant unique de Magnamalo\r\nest apparu et Ma\u00EEtre Hamon\r\nsemble en \u00EAtre m\u00E9content.\r\nKamura veut que tu t\u0027en\r\noccupes. \u003CPL\u003E,\r\n\u00E9limine ce monstre vengeur\r\net prot\u00E8ge ta patrie.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Magnamalo enrag\u00E9",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Ruggito rancoroso",
        "Client": "Ammiraglio Galleus",
        "Description": "\u00C8 apparsa una variante di\r\nMagnamalo, e il maestro Hamon\r\nsembra esserne particolarmente\r\ninfastidito. Tocca a\r\nte, \u003CPL\u003E: devi\r\ndistruggere l\u0027animo vendicativo\r\ndi quella bestia piena d\u0027odio.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Magnamalo astioso",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Mit aller Macht zur\u00FCck",
        "Client": "Galleus",
        "Description": "Eine Variante des Magnamalo ist\r\naufgetaucht. Hamon scheint besonders\r\naufgeregt zu sein. Kamura hat formell\r\ndarum gebeten, dass du dich um diese\r\nBedrohung k\u00FCmmerst, \u003CPL\u003E.\r\nBesch\u00FCtze deine Heimat und\r\neliminiere die rachs\u00FCchtige Bestie!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Tobenden Magnamalo.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "De vuelta por venganza",
        "Client": "Almirante Galleus",
        "Description": "Ha aparecido una nueva variante de\r\nMagnamalo. Tu maestro, Hamon, parece\r\nespecialmente preocupado por ello,\r\ny Kamura ha pedido oficialmente que te\r\nocupes de esta amenaza. Debes proteger\r\na tu hogar eliminando a esa bestia\r\nvengativa. \u00A1Ve y completa el trabajo!",
        "Target": "Caza un Magnamalo humillado",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0412\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F \u043C\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0438",
